.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: rose, zinnia, aconite, lily, orchid, sunflower
There 6 different types of food: cauliflower, blueberry, peach, banana, cranberry, lime
1. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person eating banana is between the person who growslily and the person who growsrose##2
4. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person who growslily is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Flower   | zinnia | sunflower | orchid | lily | aconite | rose  |
| Food           | lime | cranberry  | cauliflower | blueberry    | banana  | peach |

