.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bongani, fonseca, havana, oliveros, montecristo
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: rock, reggae, gospel, hip-hop, dubstep, blues
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the fan rock##1
2. the havana-smoker is the fan dubstep##1
3. the fan rock is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
4. the fan rock is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the fan rock##2
7. the fan reggae is on the far left##1
8. the fan gospel is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
9. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Cigar         | bongani | bolivar | montecristo      | oliveros | havana | fonseca      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | blues  | rock | hip-hop   | dubstep       | gospel |

