.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: mauve, ivory, apricot, pink, light-blue, blue
6 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, dog, fish, goat, ferret
1. the owner of the dog is the person who likes pink##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the owner of the fish is the person who likes ivory##1
5. the person who likes mauve is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the hamster and the person who likes blue##2
7. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Color        | ivory    | blue | apricot | mauve | light-blue | pink   |
| Pet   | fish | goat        | guinea-pig  | hamster     | ferret  | dog |

