.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
6 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, domino, poker, whist, bridge
The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, ship, taxi, car, helicopter
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing domino and the person playing whist##2
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
8. the person playing whist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Game   | canasta   | poker    | bridge | domino | backgammon | whist   |
| Transport         | car | trike | ship | helicopter | taxi  | jet-ski |

