.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, animation, spy, sports, martial-arts, time-travel
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, sunflower, iris, tulip, marigold
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person who growssunflower is the person watching time-travel movies##1
8. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person who growsmarigold##2
9. the person watching crime movies is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Movie-Genre    | crime | time-travel | martial-arts  | sports      | spy | animation  |
| Flower   | rose  | sunflower    | iris | dahlia | tulip | marigold |

