.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different games are played: go, chess, mah-jongg, bridge, scrabble, whist
The people have 6 different hobbies: collecting, fishing, traveling, sudoku, filmmaking, hiking
 1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person playing go is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person playing chess##2
10. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Game         | whist   | scrabble | mah-jongg       | bridge | go    | chess |
| Hobby   | fishing | filmmaking  | traveling | collecting      | sudoku | hiking        |

