 2. the polish is on the right of the turkish##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is the malaysian##1
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the polish##2
 5. the italian is between the polish and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 6. the italian is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
 8. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the polish is the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the canadian is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Sport           | biathlon      | skateboarding | cricket | basketball   | handball  | volleyball |
| Nationality   | malaysian | thai  | turkish             | polish | italian | canadian       |

