.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-13::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: yellow, lavender, mauve, amber, orange, purple
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, march, april, november, february, september
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who likes orange and the person who likes amber##2
4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who likes yellow##1
8. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Color          | mauve | lavender | yellow | orange    | purple | amber |
| Birthday   | april     | september | november   | march | december | february |

