.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-15::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, milk, soy-milk
6 different pets are kept: dog, snake, cat, guinea-pig, lizard, fish
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the snake##2
 4. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking milk is the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk    | hot-chocolate     | 7up      | almond-milk    | cola |
| Pet   | snake | dog | lizard | cat | fish | guinea-pig  |

