.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
6 different games are played: bridge, billiard, snooker, backgammon, canasta, domino
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: august, may, january, june, march, november
 1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person playing domino##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person playing domino and the person playing bridge##2
10. the person playing canasta is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Game         | backgammon | bridge | billiard | domino | canasta | snooker |
| Birthday   | august | march | january      | june     | november       | may |

 